<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1618,1933]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1799,1825]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was adequately described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[812,983,1799,1826]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="47 - 160" refId="ref38745" refString="Nielson, M. W. (1996) Two new genera and some new species of Neotropical and Oriental leafhoppers in the tribe Coelidiini (Cicadellidae: Coelidiinae). Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 122 (2 - 3), 47 - 160." type="journal article" year="1996">Nielson (1996)</bibRefCitation>
based on males and a female collected from Nilgiri Hills. Coloration and structure of s 
<emphasis box="[691,783,1835,1861]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">ubcrista</emphasis>
agreed with the description by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[1143,1315,1835,1862]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="47 - 160" refId="ref38745" refString="Nielson, M. W. (1996) Two new genera and some new species of Neotropical and Oriental leafhoppers in the tribe Coelidiini (Cicadellidae: Coelidiinae). Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 122 (2 - 3), 47 - 160." type="journal article" year="1996">Nielson (1996)</bibRefCitation>
. However, there is slight variation in configuration of the aedeagal shaft between our specimen and the original illustration by 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[151,315,1907,1933]" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="47 - 160" refId="ref38745" refString="Nielson, M. W. (1996) Two new genera and some new species of Neotropical and Oriental leafhoppers in the tribe Coelidiini (Cicadellidae: Coelidiinae). Transactions of the American Entomological Society, 122 (2 - 3), 47 - 160." type="journal article" year="1996">Nielson (1996</bibRefCitation>
: 
<figureCitation box="[325,418,1907,1933]" captionStart="FIGURES 41" captionStartId="76.[151,264,1970,1995]" captionTargetBox="[187,1380,191,1938]" captionTargetId="figure@76.[162,1425,166,1950]" captionTargetPageId="76" captionText="FIGURES 41 A–G. Singillatus parapectitus sp. nov., male genitalia.A &amp; B. Aedeagus, dorsal view; C. Aedeagus, lateral view; D. Subgenital plate, dorsal view; E. Style, dorsal view; F. Connective, dorsal view; G. Pygofer, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3366626/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Figs. 41</figureCitation>
